{"tid":126904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔埋正站上落客違巴士規例 律師：可罰$2千","createTime":"2017-02-19T16:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T00:06:43.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"533119898ad181d665d9eb7319836fca58284519","tid":126904,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:58:45.000Z","msg":"巴士車長沒有埋正站上落客引發按章工作，律師黃國桐指，巴士如在未到達巴士站便上落客，或違反《公共巴士服務規例》，「巴士未埋站就上落客，情況或等同的士喺唔可以落客嘅地方落客」。他又指交通警平日或較少針對這些情況檢控，惟他認為警方在此案上有合理依據，「咁警方唔係求其搵條『不小心駕駛』去告對方，如果係按巴士附例，（警方）係有足夠理據」。<br />\n<br />\n翻查《公共巴士服務規例》第230A章第3條《撥出地方供設置巴士站》，除列明署長可指定某個道路範圍為巴士站，亦規定專營公司的巴士或行走某指明路線的巴士，需在巴士站停車以接載或放下乘客；第9條《司機的行為》，<span style=\"color: red;\">亦指司機需停在每個巴士站。條例指如巴士公司或司機，未有在指定的巴士站停車以接載或放下乘客，即屬犯罪，可處罰款2,000元。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170220&amp;guid=56326832&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170220%26guid%3D56326832%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=0a8be263\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170220%26guid%3D56326832%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=271f7d9e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170220&amp;guid=56326832&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"9dc75c9408522acc975c8c7eb33ca693bbeddbd7","tid":126904,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:06:34.000Z","msg":"又岩喎<br />\n<br />\n道德高地, 邊夠你黎"},{"pid":"bf584a7181b9904e6aac804b39b13bc7041ddc5f","tid":126904,"uid":54104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:25:07.000Z","msg":"貼晒每個站頭, 派埋比車長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec915b0b16cb87cfd15da8c06b735fe5ecd0235","tid":126904,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T23:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd0a32c5e901406c204b7097cf20ca71de23996","tid":126904,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T23:58:10.000Z","msg":"以後繁忙時間車程長10-15分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae10b4eeba3e5401caf9cd048b024f2e6522d07d","tid":126904,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T00:02:53.000Z","msg":"以後搭巴士如果邊個巴士司機唔跟法例就上落客，我會向運輸處及巴士公司投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a923396f725681e443f3bfd4c029935cf916ef","tid":126904,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T00:03:05.000Z","msg":"咁更加要執正嚟做喇<br />\n做個奉公守法嘅市民吖嘛"},{"pid":"4af7bdb5de3e375e3a5e8e6411c1c46073ca713e","tid":126904,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T00:06:43.000Z","msg":"一早就要 以前一放學 起星光大道 近尖東上巴士 勁多旅遊巴泊左係度  基本上你唔行出馬路 巴士依為無人飛站....  支持！"}]}